SUBSTITUTE FOR
HOUSE BILL NO. 5323
A bill to amend 1984 PA 431, entitled
"The management and budget act,"
(MCL 18.1101 to 18.1594) by adding section 219a.
THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF MICHIGAN ENACT:
1 Sec. 219a. (1) The department may install 1 or more of the
2 following on state-owned buildings or critical infrastructure:
3 (a) Devices that detect unmanned aircraft.
4 (b) Technology that prevents an unauthorized unmanned aircraft
5 from flying over the state-owned building or critical
6 infrastructure.
7 (2) The department may coordinate with the state
8 transportation department to ensure that appropriate state-owned
9 buildings and critical infrastructure are included in any statewide
JJR H03709'25 (H-1) e2mo5w

2
1 geofencing database.
2 (3) This section applies only to the extent that this section
3 is not preempted by federal law.
4 (4) As used in this section:
5 (a) "Critical infrastructure" means that term as defined in
6 section 2 of the cyber civilian corps act, 2017 PA 132, MCL 18.222.
7 (b) "Unmanned aircraft" means that term as defined in section
8 3 of the unmanned aircraft systems act, 2016 PA 436, MCL 259.303.
